-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ipportfw.</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">kernel di</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Linux</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ÃƒÂ¨ implementato, ha bisogno di monitorare</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Linux</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Kernel</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">IP</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">routing dei pacchetti, le condizioni</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">stabilito dalla pacchetti di dati dell\'utente di conseguenza.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ipchains</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Ulteriori agli utenti di conoscere, nel kernel di</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Linux</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ha tre pacchetti di controllo della catena di destinazione: <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ingresso,</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">in avanti, uscita, ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ÃƒÂ¨ in procinto di pacchetti</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">in avanti</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">per l\'operazione.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ruolo ÃƒÂ¨ destinato agli utenti di selezionare l\'appropriato</span><html> FAMIGLIA: &quot;Verdana&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">&quot;server</span> web&gt; <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">server.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">LLB</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">nella scelta di quattro diversi regole, queste quattro regole per la selezione dei server per gestire le richieste degli utenti. Queste quattro norme sono</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Round-Robin <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">(RR),</span> Weighted Round-Robin <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">(WRR),</span> Least-Connection <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">(LC),</span> Weighted Least-Connection</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">(WLC).</span> Questi quattro hanno le proprie norme di adattarsi all\'ambiente.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><b>Round-Robin:</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Se la vostra scelta ÃƒÂ¨ che l\'algoritmo <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">LLB,</span> sarÃƒÂ  equamente distribuiti i pacchetti del server, ha messo tutti i server sullo stesso piano, e non pratico a prendere in considerazione le differenze tra i vari server, come ad esempio tempo di risposta, la</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">sessione</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">e il numero! Per esempio, tre server che hai <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ABC,</span> allora la distribuzione dei pacchetti di dati nell\'ordine</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">LLB</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ÃƒÂ¨</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">abcabcabc ...... ..... <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">I vantaggi di algoritmo</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Round-Robin</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ÃƒÂ¨ semplice, prendendo <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/\">il sistema</a></u> limitato di risorse, lo svantaggio ÃƒÂ¨ in grado di rilevare a quale server ha un tasso di risposta piÃƒÂ¹ alti, meno connessioni, cosÃƒÂ¬ lui ÃƒÂ¨ molto adatto per le prestazioni ambiente server.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"></span></p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><b>in-bottom-alt:</b></span> auto &quot;&gt; <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><b>Weighted Round-Robin</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Questa regola si applica agli utenti di estendere il sistema, perchÃƒÂ© ÃƒÂ¨ la performance dei server nel cluster hanno una maggiore differenza tra una definizione di server per ogni parametro ÃƒÂ¨ necessario.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Si tratta di un</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Round-Robin</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">algoritmo con parametri, il nome del parametro ÃƒÂ¨ <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">pesato.</span> ÃƒÂˆ possibile, a seconda della potenza di elaborazione del server della propria per assegnare un valore</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ponderato</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">per ogni server, maggiore ÃƒÂ¨ il valore piÃƒÂ¹ alto ÃƒÂ¨ la prioritÃƒÂ , il valore predefinito ÃƒÂ¨ <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-f