a dell\'utente. PuÃƒÂ² dare un esempio per illustrare le sue opere:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\"><br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Supponiamo che ci siano</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">n</span>-Font-family: Arial &quot;&gt; Server, tutti i server del <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">valore</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">ponderato</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">di</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Wi (i = <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">1, 2 ... N),</span> sessione</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">per la</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Ã¥Â®Â‹Ã¤Â½Â“\">Ci (i = 1, ... n), ALL-COLLEGAMENTI sessione</span> <span style=\"font-family: Ã